<h2> Task Reminder</h2>
<p>Hello <%= @task.assignee.email %>,</p>

<p>This is a reminder for your task: <strong><%= @task.title %></strong></p>

<p>Description: <%= @task.description %></p>
<p>Due Date: <%= @task.due_date.strftime('%d %B %Y, %I:%M %p') if @task.due_date %></p>

<p>Please take necessary action before it's too late.</p>
